pdqninja.util
Class TreeMultimap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
  pdqninja.util.HashMultimap<K,V>
      pdqninja.util.TreeMultimap<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Map<K,V>, SortedMap<K,V>, Multimap<K,V>, SortedMultimap<K,V>
public class TreeMultimap<K,V>
extends HashMultimap<K,V>
implements SortedMultimap<K,V>

Implementation of SortedMultimap interface as a TreeMap of mappings between key and ArrayList of values.

Although the default implementation of this class is a TreeMap of keys to ArrayList, it is possible to change both (see HashMultimap).
